erit; vertical-align: baseline; text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10.8px; padding: 15.6px 0px 5px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; font-family: \'Roboto Condensed\'; vertical-align: baseline; text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #ea1e30; text-transform: capitalize;\">Related Posts:</h3>\r\n<ol style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; list-style-position: inside; list-style-image: initial;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 6px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; list-style-type: decimal; list-style-position: inside;\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; text-decoration-line: none; outline: 0px; cursor: pointer; color: #ea1e30; transition: all 300ms ease 0s;\" title=\"DevOps l&agrave; g&igrave;? DevOps th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng nhất định phải sở hữu 6 kỹ năng v&agrave; tố chất n&agrave;y\" href=\"https://itviec.com/blog/devops-la-gi/\" rel=\"bookmark\">DevOps l&agrave; g&igrave;? DevOps th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng nhất định phải sở hữu 6 kỹ năng v&agrave; tố chất n&agrave;y</a></li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 6px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; 